/*
 * Main → Dashboard status tile for Labby.
 *
 * This stays dependency-free because it renders on every Dashboard visit.
 * It polls an authenticated, aggregate-only endpoint: no upstream URLs,
 * commands, environment names, credentials, or tool arguments cross this
 * surface. The endpoint supports both native and Incus runtime modes.
 */
